	(text "Hex Mini Driver\n\nThis is a quad output, motor driver for stepper, brushless or 2 DC motors.\nThe board comes provisioned with 2 I2C connectors for plug in rotation\nsensors AS5600 (preferably the Hex mini flex rotation sensor).\n\nTarget limits are 6-30V supply range and 5A of current.\n\nTODO for this version:\n[v] Remember to deal with the STM32 voltage reference, needs to be isolated from the amplifier.\n[v] Need pull down on BOOT0.\n[ ] Import the power FPC"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 20.32 35.814 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 2 2)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "10df153d-a61e-4111-b95d-f7a820273671")
	)
